OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FOn-demand service Bubble connects
OL,8,Fnannies and parents using its own
OL,9,Fvetting process, but not all childcare
OL,10,Fprofessionals think the system is
OL,11,Ffair, as ITV News' Cari Davies reports
OL,13,FOn-demand services now exist for
OL,14,Falmost anything - even childcare.
OL,16,FBubble, the UK's most prominent app of
OL,17,Fits kind, offers parents the chance to
OL,18,Fbook a vetted babysitter with as
OL,19,Flittle as an hour's notice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FThis service is a lifeline for parents
OL,8,Fwho praise the convenience of finding
OL,9,Flast-minute care they can trust, and
OL,10,Fcarers who have used the app to build
OL,11,Fup their own networks of families.
OL,13,FBut ITV News has heard concerns from
OL,14,Fthose working on the app, including
OL,15,Fthe use of messaging, which some
OL,16,Fcarers feel encourages them to lower
OL,17,Ftheir rates to one that can fall below
OL,18,Fminimum wage, once platform fees are
OL,19,Fdeducted.
OL,21,F'It has just made life easier'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FPaige Minier is a mum of three,
OL,8,Fincluding one-year-old twins. She
OL,9,Ffirst connected with her babysitter,
OL,10,FZahra Rizzy, through Bubble.
OL,12,FHaving previously booked nannies
OL,13,Fthrough traditional agencies, Ms
OL,14,FMinier told us platforms like these
OL,15,Foffer ease to busy parents.
OL,17,F"You don't want to say 'casual' with
OL,18,Fanything to do with childcare, because
OL,19,Fobviously these are my kids and I'm
OL,20,Fabsolutely obsessed about making sure
OL,21,Fthey're safe," she told us.
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"But that ability to be able to look
OL,8,Fif you're in a pinch and you need a
OL,9,Flittle extra help, and have that at
OL,10,Fyour fingertips and not have to go
OL,11,Fthrough long, drawn-out calls where
OL,12,Fthey're listing stuff and putting CVs
OL,13,Fout, makes it quite enjoyable.
OL,15,F"It's like where you can book all the
OL,16,Fother things on demand, it just made
OL,17,Flife easier."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FLiving in London away from family and
OL,8,Ffriends in the US, Ms Minier said
OL,9,FBubble helped her find childcare she
OL,10,Fcould trust in a city where she didn't
OL,11,Fhave an existing network.
OL,13,FBubble and similar apps occupy a space
OL,14,Fbetween a traditional nanny agency and
OL,15,Fmore informal methods of finding care,
OL,16,Fsuch as social media groups.
OL,18,F"It is this nice in between where it
OL,19,Fdoesn't feel so formal, but it doesn't
OL,20,Ffeel so hypercasual that you're just
OL,21,Fon an online group," Ms Minier told us.
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"Nannies are background checked, so
OL,8,Fyou can really read their background
OL,9,Fand understand their experience. So
OL,10,Fit's a happy middle ground, I would
OL,11,Fsay."
OL,13,FHer nanny swears by the app. Ms Rizzy
OL,14,Fhas spent four years building a
OL,15,Fchildcare career through Bubble,
OL,16,Fworking with around 150 different
OL,17,Ffamilies in London.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
