FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"I decide what schedule I want to
OL,8,Fwork, I can put myself as available on
OL,9,Fthe app, and they also have this
OL,10,Finstant book(ing) setting, where new
OL,11,Ffamilies and the regular families I
OL,12,Fwork for can instantly book me," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"I feel like it cuts out the middle
OL,16,Fperson, so it's quite nice for me
OL,17,Fpersonally to find families myself to
OL,18,Fsee which ones I connect with and get
OL,19,Falong with rather than having an
OL,20,Fagency.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@MpmrD@QpntD@`O]wD@AOU
