OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"It's definitely much quicker."
OL,9,F'Trusted childcare near you'
OL,11,FPlatforms like Bubble have stepped
OL,12,Finto what has otherwise been an
OL,13,Findustry characterised by
OL,14,Ffragmentation and a lack of
OL,15,Fregulation, with many finding work on
OL,16,Fsocial media groups or via word of
OL,17,Fmouth.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@_O]
