CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FAlmost 50% of nannies and babysitters
OL,8,Fin England describe the job market as
OL,9,F"poor" or "very poor", according to a
OL,10,Fsurvey of hundreds of workers carried
OL,11,Fout by the National Nanny Association.
OL,13,FSome 67% describe a lack of full-time
OL,14,Fnanny roles, while around a quarter of
OL,15,Fthose surveyed said they are turning
OL,16,Fto online platforms to find work.
OL,18,FBubble describes itself as the UK's
OL,19,Fnumber one trusted family support app.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@FO]qD@KOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FSince it was launched in 2016, the
OL,8,Fplatform has connected at least
OL,9,F300,000 parents with around 30,000
OL,10,Fsitters, with some three million hours
OL,11,Fof childcare booked.
OL,13,FCEO Ari Last told us part of the
OL,14,Fplatform's mission is to help parents
OL,15,Fregain their social life.
OL,17,F"It's easily trivialised, but it is a
OL,18,Fmassive issue for parents," Mr Last
OL,19,Ftold us.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"Bubble is an enabler for them to get
OL,8,Fback that freedom, that flexibility."
OL,10,FParents on Bubble can set up an
OL,11,Faccount and advertise a job, which
OL,12,Fsitters can then apply for.
OL,14,FSitters are screened and vetted by the
OL,15,Fapp's own multi-step process,
OL,16,Finvolving checks on their ID,
OL,17,Fbackground, right to work and
OL,18,Freferencing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FNannies are not required to have a DBS
OL,8,Fcheck, but can indicate whether they
OL,9,Fhave one on their profiles.
OL,11,FThose looking for work can then apply
OL,12,Fto jobs, setting their own rate. Once
OL,13,Fa sit with a family is complete,
OL,14,Fpayment is received within 72 hours.
OL,16,FWant to share your story? Email
OL,17,Fyourstory@itn.co.uk
OL,19,F'I don't know how it's fair'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FTalana Oliveira, a childcare
OL,8,Fprofessional who used to use Bubble,
OL,9,Fbelieves the concept of the app is
OL,10,Fpositive - but has concerns around pay.
OL,12,FITV News has seen several examples of
OL,13,Fan information banner appearing when a
OL,14,Fuser is applying to a job advertised
OL,15,Fon the app.
OL,17,FThe message reads: "Heads Up: 80% of
OL,18,Fsitters who get booked are between #12-
OL,19,F15 per hour".
OL,26,@yD@TOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FSeveral carers have told ITV News the
OL,8,Fprompt makes them feel as though they
OL,9,Fshould drop their hourly rate to
OL,10,Fprices within this bracket, some of
OL,11,Fwhich can fall below minimum wage once
OL,12,FBubble fees are subtracted.
OL,14,FWhen the standard platform fees are
OL,15,Fdeducted, which are 15% for the first
OL,16,Fjob with a family and 7% for future
OL,17,Fsits, potential rates within this
OL,18,Fbracket can fall below the national
OL,19,Fminimum wage - currently #12.71 per
OL,20,Fhour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FFor example, a standard sitter would
OL,8,Fonly earn minimum wage if they charged
OL,9,Fat least #14.95 for an initial sit.
OL,10,FFor any sits booked with the same
OL,11,Ffamily thereafter, they would need to
OL,12,Fcharge at least #13.67.
OL,14,FAs an online marketplace, Bubble does
OL,15,Fnot have the same legal obligations
OL,16,Faround minimum wage as traditional
OL,17,Femployers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FThe app claims the average hourly rate
OL,8,Fon the app is around #15 a hour, and
OL,9,Fhas told us the average platform fee
OL,10,Fsits at around 6%, due to lower repeat-
OL,11,Fbooking fees offered to some carers.
OL,13,FMs Oliveira told us she had seen
OL,14,Fsimilar messaging on the platform.
OL,16,F"It's fair that they are letting you
OL,17,Fknow," she said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"But if you are new in the app,
OL,8,Fthey'll send you these 'tips', and
OL,9,Fyou're going to lower your price, so
OL,10,Fyou kind of make the whole industry
OL,11,Flower their prices as well.
OL,13,F"I don't know how it's fair with the
OL,14,Fjob that you do, you have to
OL,15,Fspecialise, it's a child. You're
OL,16,Ftaking care of another life.
OL,18,F"Maybe it'll take ages to find a job,
OL,19,Fand sometimes you're going to be
OL,20,Fpanicking and lowering your price as
OL,21,Fwell."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F'It's not a race to the bottom on
OL,8,Fprice'
OL,10,FWe put these concerns to Ari Last in
OL,11,Fan interview, the founder and CEO of
OL,12,FBubble, including showing him the
OL,13,Fprompts we had seen.
OL,15,FHe said: "The beauty of the platform
OL,16,Ffor sitters is they have complete
OL,17,Fcontrol and flexibility to set their
OL,18,Fown rates.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,F"The really nice thing that we're
OL,8,Fproud of is how the best sitters on
OL,9,Fthe app doing the most work actually
OL,10,Fhave higher rates than others, which
OL,11,Ftells you it's not a race to the
OL,12,Fbottom.
OL,14,F"We absolutely believe sitters should
OL,15,Fbe paid not only minimum wage, they
OL,16,Fshould be paid well because they're
OL,17,Fdoing an incredible job and they're
OL,18,Fgenerally underpaid in this industry."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/22
