OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780675875
OL,3,CChildcare apps change the game for
OL,4,Cparents - but some raise concerns for
OL,5,Ccarers
OL,7,FMr Last told us that he met dozens of
OL,8,Fnannies and sitters before the app was
OL,9,Fofficially launched a decade ago.
OL,11,F"These are fantastic people looking to
OL,12,Fdo what they love, often meet more
OL,13,Fparents, earn more money and to do it
OL,14,Fsafely and securely," he said.
OL,16,F"We've been really focused as well on
OL,17,Fbuilding a really trusted, great
OL,18,Fexperience for parents, equally on how
OL,19,Fdo we build something that's going to
OL,20,Fwork and be valuable for sitters as
OL,21,Fwell."
