OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIn a statement following our
OL,13,Finterview, the company told us: "We've
OL,14,Falways championed the idea that
OL,15,Fchildcarers should be paid well for
OL,16,Fthe critical service they provide, and
OL,17,Fwe're proud of how Bubble has
OL,18,Fsupported thousands of sitters to earn
OL,19,Fmore ` safely, conveniently and on
OL,20,Ftheir terms.
